data.description: Prelisting inspection report available to buyer, Ask a realtor for details. Needing to upsize? 8630 Monclova Rd features a 5 Bedrooms, 2 Bathrooms, and is a ranch style home reaching 2855 SQFT in living space. Since 2015, upgrades include new Drywall, Doors, Carpet, Vapor Barrier, Furnace, HWT and both bathrooms. 28x25 great room with cathedral ceilings & fireplace great for hosting events. Craft room of the back of the home for all hobbies. 2 car garage in the back of the property has newer door. Home warranty offered with this home. Book your appointment :)
